## TypeScript Best Practices

### Type Definitions
```typescript
// ‚úÖ Good: Clear interface definitions
interface User {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  email: string;
  preferences: UserPreferences;
}

interface UserPreferences {
  theme: 'light' | 'dark' | 'system';
  notifications: boolean;
  language: string;
}

// ‚ùå Bad: Loose typing
